Metallic high chemical purity (>99.9%) thorium foils

targets. Each foil (17x50 mm2) was placed between
aluminum (100+-4 mu-m thickness) and copper (40+-2 mu-m
thickness) foils for beam intensity monitoring. The
three foils were inserted into a plastic frame and
wrapped in 10 mu-m thick aluminium foil.
